# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:22
translate spanish hwb_s36_ffcc7f14:

    # "Fading light from the sunset wakes me up."
    "La luz que se desvanece del atardecer me despierta."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:24
translate spanish hwb_s36_5a4ec086:

    # "After reuniting, the first thing Marina and I did was take a nap."
    "Después de reunirnos, lo primero que hicimos Marina y yo fue tomar una siesta."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:26
translate spanish hwb_s36_65813afc:

    # "For the first time, we slept in the same bed, both of us too tired to do anything more than gaze into each other's eyes as we drifted off."
    "Por primera vez, dormimos en la misma cama, ambas demasiado cansadas para hacer algo más que mirarnos a los ojos mientras nos quedábamos dormidas."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:28
translate spanish hwb_s36_70a7fe21:

    # "Now, hours later, we're still in the same spot. One of Marina's hands clings to my shirt, while she's pressed up against my side."
    "Ahora, horas después, seguimos en el mismo lugar. Una de las manos de Marina se aferra a mi camisa, mientras está presionada contra mi costado."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:30
translate spanish hwb_s36_271513b3:

    # "Her breath, shallow and steady, is warm against my neck."
    "Su respiración, superficial y constante, es cálida contra mi cuello."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:32
translate spanish hwb_s36_a2dc7905:

    # "I feel like I could stay here all day. Or for a week. A year. Whatever. Just enjoying this closeness."
    "Siento que podría quedarme aquí todo el día. O una semana. Un año. Lo que sea. Solo disfrutando esta cercanía."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:34
translate spanish hwb_s36_88c85789:

    # "Marina sighs in her sleep, shifting a little but not moving too far away. I watch her, a small smile dancing on my lips."
    "Marina suspira mientras duerme, se mueve un poco pero no se aleja demasiado. La observo, una pequeña sonrisa baila en mis labios."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:36
translate spanish hwb_s36_8bb354a8:

    # "No way we’re gonna be able to sleep tonight after taking naps this late. We can probably head out and get to the festival site a bit early."
    "No hay manera de que podamos dormir esta noche después de tomar siestas tan tarde. Probablemente podamos salir y llegar al sitio del festival un poco temprano."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:38
translate spanish hwb_s36_b2a840ac:

    # "Beat the lines to get in and maybe end up closer to the stage."
    "Evitar las filas para entrar y quizás terminar más cerca del escenario."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:40
translate spanish hwb_s36_c1123a2b:

    # "I’ll see how she feels when she gets up."
    "Veré cómo se siente cuando se despierte."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:42
translate spanish hwb_s36_9bb326cb:

    # "Gently, I extract myself from her grip and climb out of bed."
    "Suavemente, me libero de su agarre y me levanto de la cama."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:44
translate spanish hwb_s36_29ba5491:

    # "To kill some time, I wander to the back to take stock of our supplies."
    "Para matar el tiempo, deambulo hacia atrás para hacer inventario de nuestros suministros."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:46
translate spanish hwb_s36_ce623245:

    # "We’re running low on bottled water, and could use some more snacks. The healthy kind, not the Marina-selected, tooth-rotting kind."
    "Se nos está acabando el agua embotellada, y nos vendrían bien más bocadillos. De los saludables, no de los que selecciona Marina, que pudren los dientes."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:48
translate spanish hwb_s36_74f31106:

    # "Also, we need to stop by a laundromat sometime, too. Hell, we should probably go to a clothing store and pick up a few more changes of clothes for Marina."
    "También, necesitamos pasar por una lavandería en algún momento. Diablos, probablemente deberíamos ir a una tienda de ropa y comprarle a Marina un par de mudas más."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:50
translate spanish hwb_s36_6372db94:

    # "Since we’re gonna be sticking together and all."
    "Ya que vamos a estar juntas y todo."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:52
translate spanish hwb_s36_54ff7a94:

    # "That thought makes me smile, so happy that I couldn’t stop even if I wanted to."
    "Ese pensamiento me hace sonreír, tan feliz que no podría parar aunque quisiera."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:54
translate spanish hwb_s36_5b52817e:

    # "I don’t have to be lonely anymore. I can make these plans for two."
    "Ya no tengo que estar sola. Puedo hacer estos planes para dos."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:56
translate spanish hwb_s36_a02a95b0:

    # "When I walk back by the bed, still being careful not to disturb Marina, I notice something weird."
    "Cuando vuelvo a pasar junto a la cama, aún con cuidado de no molestar a Marina, noto algo extraño."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:58
translate spanish hwb_s36_3fa5e5b4:

    # "It’s gotten brighter outside."
    "Se ha vuelto más brillante afuera."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:60
translate spanish hwb_s36_bcb53d3a:

    # "No way."
    "No puede ser."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:62
translate spanish hwb_s36_729eb635:

    # "It dawns on me, quite literally:"
    "Me doy cuenta, literalmente:"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:64
translate spanish hwb_s36_c59876a6:

    # "We didn’t just sleep through the day."
    "No solo dormimos durante el día."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:66
translate spanish hwb_s36_73af442f:

    # "We slept all the way through the night and into the next morning."
    "Dormimos toda la noche y hasta la mañana siguiente."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:68
translate spanish hwb_s36_56b929f4:

    # Amber "Marina!"
    Amber "Марина!"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:70
translate spanish hwb_s36_c9e8f55f:

    # "I shout her name as I lunge across the bed to shake her shoulder."
    "Grito su nombre mientras me lanzo sobre la cama para sacudirle el hombro."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:72
translate spanish hwb_s36_88516185:

    # "Despite my frenzy, she opens her eyes lazily.."
    "A pesar de mi frenesí, abre los ojos con pereza."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:74
translate spanish hwb_s36_252ed066:

    # Marina "Amber?"
    Marina "Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:76
translate spanish hwb_s36_55fac5ba:

    # Marina "What’s wrong?"
    Marina "Что-то случилось?"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:78
translate spanish hwb_s36_9bac0fa7:

    # Amber "We slept way too late. We’ve gotta get going fast. The festival’s starting in just a few hours."
    Amber "Мы слишком сильно проспали. Нам нужно быстро собираться. Фестиваль начнется через несколько часов."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:80
translate spanish hwb_s36_93469e0d:

    # "Marina pats my head like I’m a naive kid."
    "Marina me acaricia la cabeza como si fuera una niña ingenua."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:82
translate spanish hwb_s36_55655d24:

    # Marina "Amber, it’s okay, that’s not until tomorrow."
    Marina "Эмбер, все в порядке фестиваль завтра."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:84
translate spanish hwb_s36_b7de1d2d:

    # Amber "It is tomorrow! We slept all night."
    Amber "Сейчас уже “Завтра”! Мы проспали всю ночь."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:86
translate spanish hwb_s36_2bd3f691:

    # "Now her eyes get a bit bigger, and right on time the sunlight falls across her face."
    "Ahora sus ojos se abren un poco más, y justo a tiempo la luz del sol le cae en la cara."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:88
translate spanish hwb_s36_5b48006b:

    # Marina "Huh?"
    Marina "Что?"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:90
translate spanish hwb_s36_defadd0a:

    # Amber "Yeah."
    Amber "Ага."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:92
translate spanish hwb_s36_0732340f:

    # "I move back, letting her sit up."
    "Me echo hacia atrás, dejando que se siente."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:94
translate spanish hwb_s36_9500fb75:

    # Amber "We’ve gotta go, or we’ll be standing in line all day."
    Amber "Мы должны ехать, иначе простоим в очереди весь день."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:96
translate spanish hwb_s36_ac2a5c4e:

    # "She smooshes her fists into her eyes and rolls out of bed."
    "Se frota los puños contra los ojos y se sale rodando de la cama."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:100
translate spanish hwb_s36_b284c766:

    # Marina "I’m up, I’m up."
    Marina "Встаю, встаю."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:102
translate spanish hwb_s36_ba7dda58:

    # Marina "Can you make some coffee, please?"
    Marina "Можешь сделать кофе, пожалуйста?"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s36_5ed1a33e:

    # Amber "No prob."
    Amber "Без проблем."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:118
translate spanish hwb_s36_fa35aa51:

    # Marina "Gonna get ready."
    Marina "Пойду собираться."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:120
translate spanish hwb_s36_f1738300:

    # "I nod. Marina zombie-shuffles off to the bathroom to brush her teeth and fix her hair. I set about preparing."
    "Asiento. Marina se arrastra como zombie al baño para lavarse los dientes y arreglarse el cabello. Yo me pongo a preparar."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:122
translate spanish hwb_s36_3b99fbc6:

    # "Soon, the warm smell of brewing coffee fills the air, as does the sound of running water. Both Marina and the coffee finish around the same time."
    "Pronto, el cálido aroma del café recién hecho llena el aire, junto con el sonido del agua corriendo. Tanto Marina como el café terminan casi al mismo tiempo."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:130
translate spanish hwb_s36_7855122f:

    # "Marina skips over to where I am and leans into my shoulder, while I wrap an arm around her."
    "Marina salta hasta donde estoy y se recuesta en mi hombro, mientras yo la rodeo con un brazo."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:132
translate spanish hwb_s36_a03061e6:

    # Marina "Sorry, I shouldn’t hold us up, huh?"
    Marina "Извини, наверное, не стоит нас задерживать всякими нежностями, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:134
translate spanish hwb_s36_23bc8a60:

    # Amber "Nah, this is okay."
    Amber "Ничего, все в порядке."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:136
translate spanish hwb_s36_a93fefa2:

    # "Just for a moment."
    "Solo por un momento."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s36_7a5f096b:

    # "Then I pull away and grab a pair of mugs, passing one to Marina. I fill mine up with steaming black coffee, then hand her the creamer and sugar."
    "Luego me aparto y agarro un par de tazas, pasándole una a Marina. Lleno la mía con café negro humeante, y luego le doy la crema y el azúcar."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:147
translate spanish hwb_s36_5b102965:

    # "But Marina shakes her head."
    "Pero Marina niega con la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s36_e7149bf7:

    # Marina "I’ll try it how you drink it."
    Marina "Я попробую выпить его так, как ты пьешь."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:153
translate spanish hwb_s36_feb8d935:

    # "Eyebrows raised, I pour her a cup."
    "Con las cejas levantadas, le sirvo una taza."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s36_b2a91654:

    # Amber "You sure? It’s a super acquired taste."
    Amber "Ты уверена? У него весьма специфичный вкус."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:159
translate spanish hwb_s36_f7ba9122:

    # "Marina takes a sip and scrunches up her face in disgust."
    "Marina da un sorbo y arruga la cara con disgusto."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s36_c87a563d:

    # Marina "It’s good!"
    Marina "Неплохо!"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:167
translate spanish hwb_s36_6011ecd2:

    # Amber "Uh huh."
    Amber "Ну конечно."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:171
translate spanish hwb_s36_bd5bf4cf:

    # Marina "No, really!"
    Marina "Нет, правда!"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:175
translate spanish hwb_s36_fd13c374:

    # "She chokes on her next sip."
    "Se atraganta con el siguiente sorbo."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:179
translate spanish hwb_s36_2c5e2a21:

    # Amber "You don’t have to drink it black just because I do, you know."
    Amber "Слушай, тебе не обязательно пить чистый кофе только потому, что так делаю я."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:183
translate spanish hwb_s36_b0bf7660:

    # Marina "You said it’s an acquired taste though, right? So I wanna acquire that taste."
    Marina "Помнишь, ты сказала, что у него специфичный вкус? Так вот, я хочу распробовать его."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:187
translate spanish hwb_s36_f11d52dc:

    # Amber "Right."
    Amber "Ладно."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s36_dc3cf6b7:

    # "By the time I’ve finished my first cup, she’s only had a quarter of hers."
    "Para cuando terminé mi primera taza, ella solo había tomado un cuarto de la suya."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s36_4c77e684:

    # "She gets halfway through before she gives up and dumps in some sugar."
    "Llega a la mitad antes de rendirse y echarle un poco de azúcar."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:195
translate spanish hwb_s36_86a111ff:

    # Marina "I’ll acquire it later."
    Marina "Я познакомлюсь с его спецификой позже."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s36_caca9aad:

    # Amber "Of course."
    Amber "Как скажешь."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:206
translate spanish hwb_s36_4ceba150:

    # "While she preps her coffee, I go over to the cabinet where we stash the gold. Aside from those, there’s one other small, brightly decorated box."
    "Mientras prepara su café, voy al armario donde guardamos el oro. Además de eso, hay una caja pequeña y decorada con colores brillantes."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s36_c9919b66:

    # "I take it out and set it on the counter. Marina instantly hops over."
    "Lo saco y lo pongo sobre el mostrador. Marina salta al instante."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:218
translate spanish hwb_s36_258006c8:

    # Marina "Ooh, what’s that?"
    Marina "О, что это такое?"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:220
translate spanish hwb_s36_0f0d49d8:

    # "Inside are two wristbands made of soft fabric. They’re our entrance passes to the festival."
    "Adentro hay dos pulseras de tela suave. Son nuestros pases de entrada al festival."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:224
translate spanish hwb_s36_46a7cf54:

    # "I pass one to Marina."
    "Le paso una a Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:226
translate spanish hwb_s36_3b9dde7e:

    # "Hers. {w=1.5}Gramps’."
    "La suya. {w=1.5}La del Abuelo."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:230
translate spanish hwb_s36_2426aaec:

    # "The tenderness with which she takes it reminds me of when she first held the gold. Like if it fell, it would break."
    "La ternura con la que la toma me recuerda a cuando sostuvo el oro por primera vez. Como si se fuera a romper si caía."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:234
translate spanish hwb_s36_4969d0dc:

    # Amber "Make sure you don’t lose it, or you’ll have to wait in the RV while I go watch."
    Amber "Смотри не потеряй, иначе тебе придется ждать в трейлере, пока я буду веселиться на фестивале."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:238
translate spanish hwb_s36_2c27bd16:

    # Marina "You wouldn’t!"
    Marina "Ты не посмеешь!"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:242
translate spanish hwb_s36_ac2feadc:

    # "I think about it for a second."
    "Lo pienso por un segundo."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:244
translate spanish hwb_s36_6207f408:

    # "Then I answer, truthfully."
    "Luego respondo, con sinceridad."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s36_dab3a57a:

    # Amber "Okay, you’re right."
    Amber "Да, ты права."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:252
translate spanish hwb_s36_85942956:

    # Amber "But still."
    Amber "Но все же...."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:256
translate spanish hwb_s36_99829771:

    # "There’s a little thing that hangs off the wristband, and Marina pulls to tighten it. Then she leans over and kisses my cheek."
    "Hay una pequeña pieza que cuelga de la pulsera, y Marina tira para ajustarla. Luego se inclina y me besa en la mejilla."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:260
translate spanish hwb_s36_841d53a1:

    # Marina "I won’t."
    Marina "Я не потеряю."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:262
translate spanish hwb_s36_14582372:

    # "I slide mine on and tighten it as well, putting the box back in its safe spot."
    "Me pongo la mía y la ajusto también, guardando la caja en su lugar seguro."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:266
translate spanish hwb_s36_5c53822b:

    # "There’s a lump in my throat, over how it was always supposed to be me and Gramps who went."
    "Siento un nudo en la garganta, porque siempre se suponía que íbamos el Abuelo y yo."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:268
translate spanish hwb_s36_340e4324:

    # "Marina touches my hand, and she smiles."
    "Marina toca mi mano y sonríe."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:272
translate spanish hwb_s36_985b8804:

    # "I smile back."
    "Le devuelvo la sonrisa."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:274
translate spanish hwb_s36_94be7345:

    # "This is just as good, though."
    "Pero esto también está bien."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:276
translate spanish hwb_s36_552271f1:

    # "I swallow my sadness before it can take over and lead the way up to the front of the RV."
    "Trago mi tristeza antes de que me domine y guío el camino hacia el frente de la casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:278
translate spanish hwb_s36_246795b4:

    # Amber "You ready?"
    Amber "Готова?"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:282
translate spanish hwb_s36_0150462e:

    # Marina "Hell yeah!"
    Marina "Да, черт побери!"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:284
translate spanish hwb_s36_e0e63d5d:

    # Amber "Let’s get this show on the road, then."
    Amber "Тогда погнали."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:324
translate spanish hwb_s36_40e92d3c:

    # "The motorhome grumbles as I turn the key, but the engine catches."
    "La casa rodante gruñe cuando giro la llave, pero el motor arranca."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:326
translate spanish hwb_s36_5e5f7ce8:

    # "I wait a second to see if it’s going to die, but it doesn’t. Though the whole thing shakes a little more than I’m used to."
    "Espero un segundo para ver si se va a apagar, pero no lo hace. Aunque todo tiembla un poco más de lo que estoy acostumbrada."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s36_57ec972c:

    # "Slowly, I navigate out of the parking lot and back onto the main streets. It may be early, but there are lots of people out and about."
    "Lentamente, salgo del estacionamiento y vuelvo a las calles principales. Puede que sea temprano, pero hay mucha gente por ahí."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:340
translate spanish hwb_s36_93558e68:

    # "Traffic is thick, with a lot of the people probably going to Coachella."
    "El tráfico es denso, con mucha gente probablemente yendo a Coachella."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:344
translate spanish hwb_s36_f311c5dc:

    # Amber "See, this is why I wanted to leave early. It’s normally only a half hour drive, but this is crazy."
    Amber "Видишь? Вот поэтому я хотела выехать пораньше. Туда можно добраться буквально за пол часа, но то, что творится сейчас на дороге просто безумие."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:348
translate spanish hwb_s36_98d2624a:

    # Marina "Think we’re all going to the same place?"
    Marina "Думаешь, мы все едем в одно место?"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:350
translate spanish hwb_s36_50372813:

    # Amber "Maybe. At least a few."
    Amber "Может быть. По крайней мере, таких достаточно."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:354
translate spanish hwb_s36_063017ff:

    # "Marina laughs."
    "Marina se ríe."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:358
translate spanish hwb_s36_5f1d9671:

    # Amber "What?"
    Amber "Что?"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:362
translate spanish hwb_s36_43ee99e3:

    # Marina "I just think it’s kind of funny that this has happened the whole time. With the treasure and stuff."
    Marina "Просто забавно, что такое постоянно происходит с нами. Как, например, с сокровищем и прочим."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:366
translate spanish hwb_s36_06addd72:

    # Marina "Everywhere we go it’s like, traffic jam after traffic jam."
    Marina "Куда бы мы ни поехали  - везде одни пробки."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:370
translate spanish hwb_s36_fb3aca57:

    # Amber "Yeah, you’re right. Should be better after this, though."
    Amber "Да, ты права. Но дальше должно быть побыстрее."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:374
translate spanish hwb_s36_30efcaf4:

    # Marina "Yeah, it will be."
    Marina "Да, должно."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:376
translate spanish hwb_s36_0d59ef66:

    # "We creep along until we reach a totaled car. Doesn’t look like anyone was hurt, but it’s the reason traffic is so slow."
    "Avanzamos lentamente hasta llegar a un coche destrozado. No parece que nadie haya resultado herido, pero es la razón del tráfico lento."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:378
translate spanish hwb_s36_37ed895c:

    # "Once we get past, I can finally openly accelerate. The new and improved engine pulls its weight; everything is much smoother and quieter."
    "Una vez que pasamos, por fin puedo acelerar sin problema. El motor nuevo y mejorado rinde bien; todo es mucho más suave y silencioso."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:380
translate spanish hwb_s36_a8e70fab:

    # "Soon, the city of Indio comes into view. Super close to the California and Arizona border, Coachella is held just a few miles east of town."
    "Pronto, la ciudad de Indio aparece a la vista. Muy cerca de la frontera entre California y Arizona, Coachella se celebra a solo unos kilómetros al este del pueblo."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:382
translate spanish hwb_s36_dd3e3ef4:

    # "As we get closer and closer, our anticipation builds. It’s easy to read Marina, since she’s bouncing and fidgeting in her seat."
    "A medida que nos acercamos, nuestra anticipación crece. Es fácil leer a Marina, porque no para de saltar y moverse en su asiento."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:384
translate spanish hwb_s36_bb7c390d:

    # "I’m more composed, but I feel it too."
    "Yo estoy más serena, pero también lo siento."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:390
translate spanish hwb_s36_60038f40:

    # "We glance at each other, at the exact same time, and grin. We’ve been doing that a lot lately."
    "Nos miramos, exactamente al mismo tiempo, y sonreímos. Hemos estado haciendo eso mucho últimamente."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:396
translate spanish hwb_s36_093f0a7f:

    # "At last, the huge line of trees that borders the festival grounds stands just ahead."
    "Por fin, la enorme hilera de árboles que bordea los terrenos del festival está justo adelante."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:398
translate spanish hwb_s36_faf41b18:

    # "I take the exit and join yet another long line of cars heading for the parking area and campground."
    "Tomo la salida y me uno a otra larga fila de autos que se dirigen al área de estacionamiento y campamento."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:400
translate spanish hwb_s36_4b12a2c8:

    # "Guests carrying coolers, chairs and camping supplies crowd the edges of the unpaved roads, making us slow down."
    "Los invitados cargando hieleras, sillas y suministros de campamento abarrotan los bordes de los caminos sin pavimentar, haciéndonos reducir la velocidad."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:409
translate spanish hwb_s36_03675a73:

    # "Finally, we find a spot and I kill the engine."
    "Finalmente, encontramos un lugar y apago el motor."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:413
translate spanish hwb_s36_46769365:

    # "Marina looks at me, waiting for me to say something."
    "Marina me mira, esperando que diga algo."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:417
translate spanish hwb_s36_accd30be:

    # "But I’m all out of cheesy speeches. So I just grab her hand, and we both stand up."
    "Pero ya no me quedan discursos cursis. Así que solo tomo su mano, y ambas nos levantamos."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:421
translate spanish hwb_s36_1925a7d2:

    # Amber "Let’s go."
    Amber "Пойдем."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:73
translate spanish hwb_s36_c48159af:

    # "Despite my frenzy, she opens her eyes lazily."
    "A pesar de mi frenesí, ella abre los ojos con pereza."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:257
translate spanish hwb_s36_78928843:

    # "There’s a little tag that hangs off the wristband, and Marina pulls to tighten it. Then she leans over and kisses my cheek."
    "Hay una pequeña etiqueta que cuelga de la pulsera, y Marina tira para ajustarla. Luego se inclina y besa mi mejilla."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s36_eff85064:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_56b929f4"
    # Amber "Marina!"
    voice "hwb_s36adult_56b929f4"
    Amber "Марина!"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s36_4050ca8c:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_9bac0fa7"
    # Amber "We slept way too late. We’ve gotta get going fast. The festival’s starting in just a few hours."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_9bac0fa7"
    Amber "Мы слишком сильно проспали. Нам нужно быстро собираться. Фестиваль начнется через несколько часов."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s36_5eb14c49:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_b7de1d2d"
    # Amber "It is tomorrow! We slept all night."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_b7de1d2d"
    Amber "Сейчас уже “Завтра”! Мы проспали всю ночь."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:99
translate spanish hwb_s36_e5147a25:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_defadd0a"
    # Amber "Yeah."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_defadd0a"
    Amber "Ага."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:105
translate spanish hwb_s36_e569775c:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_9500fb75"
    # Amber "We’ve gotta go, or we’ll be standing in line all day."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_9500fb75"
    Amber "Мы должны ехать, иначе простоим в очереди весь день."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:124
translate spanish hwb_s36_69d2adb3:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_5ed1a33e"
    # Amber "No prob."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_5ed1a33e"
    Amber "Без проблем."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s36_9de48d02:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_23bc8a60"
    # Amber "Nah, this is okay."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_23bc8a60"
    Amber "Ничего, все в порядке."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:174
translate spanish hwb_s36_906f3e25:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_b2a91654"
    # Amber "You sure? It’s a super acquired taste."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_b2a91654"
    Amber "Ты уверена? У него весьма специфичный вкус."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:188
translate spanish hwb_s36_951b70c3:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_6011ecd2"
    # Amber "Uh huh."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_6011ecd2"
    Amber "Ну конечно."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:202
translate spanish hwb_s36_ec795ea0:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_2c5e2a21"
    # Amber "You don’t have to drink it black just because I do, you know."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_2c5e2a21"
    Amber "Слушай, тебе не обязательно пить чистый кофе только потому, что так делаю я."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:212
translate spanish hwb_s36_6ecad8c3:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_f11d52dc"
    # Amber "Right."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_f11d52dc"
    Amber "Ладно."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:226
translate spanish hwb_s36_a6141049:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_caca9aad"
    # Amber "Of course."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_caca9aad"
    Amber "Как скажешь."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:265
translate spanish hwb_s36_d53282a0:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_4969d0dc"
    # Amber "Make sure you don’t lose it, or you’ll have to wait in the RV while I go watch."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_4969d0dc"
    Amber "Смотри не потеряй, иначе тебе придется ждать в трейлере, пока я буду веселиться на фестивале."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:281
translate spanish hwb_s36_a691f622:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_dab3a57a"
    # Amber "Okay, you’re right."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_dab3a57a"
    Amber "Да, ты права."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s36_d850b8ed:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_85942956"
    # Amber "But still."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_85942956"
    Amber "Но все же...."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:315
translate spanish hwb_s36_ab55b8fb:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_246795b4"
    # Amber "You ready?"
    voice "hwb_s36adult_246795b4"
    Amber "Готова?"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:323
translate spanish hwb_s36_fab7d6e5:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_e0e63d5d"
    # Amber "Let’s get this show on the road, then."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_e0e63d5d"
    Amber "Тогда погнали."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:387
translate spanish hwb_s36_59b25833:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_f311c5dc"
    # Amber "See, this is why I wanted to leave early. It’s normally only a half hour drive, but this is crazy."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_f311c5dc"
    Amber "Видишь? Вот поэтому я хотела выехать пораньше. Туда можно добраться буквально за пол часа, но то, что творится сейчас на дороге просто безумие."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:395
translate spanish hwb_s36_5a458646:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_50372813"
    # Amber "Maybe. At least a few."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_50372813"
    Amber "Может быть. По крайней мере, таких достаточно."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:405
translate spanish hwb_s36_6223bc89:

    # "hwb_s36adult_5f1d9671"
    "hwb_s36adult_5f1d9671"

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:419
translate spanish hwb_s36_9f1a0f9b:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_fb3aca57"
    # Amber "Yeah, you’re right. Should be better after this, though."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_fb3aca57"
    Amber "Да, ты права. Но дальше должно быть побыстрее."

# game/script/hwb_s36.rpy:472
translate spanish hwb_s36_f262c013:

    # voice "hwb_s36adult_1925a7d2"
    # Amber "Let’s go."
    voice "hwb_s36adult_1925a7d2"
    Amber "Пойдем."

